This project focuses on automating Paxi performance reporting using Power BI. The dashboard tracks key KPIs such as AHT, CSAT, rejected calls, and missed calls.

Purpose:
To provide real-time visibility of agent performance, support quick coaching, and identify underperforming agents based on KPIs.

Tools Used:

* Power BI
* Excel

Key Features:

* Automated KPI tracking
* Agent-level performance breakdown
* Coaching insights for performance improvement
